Testing #15359

See the following snippet

```
var express = require('express');
var router = express.Router();

/* GET home page. */
router.get('/', function (req, res, next) {
  let object = someFunction();
  res.render('index', { title: 'Express' });
});


function someFunction() {
  return [1, 2, 3];
}

module.exports = router;
```

When I have a break point on the following line
` let object = someFunction();` 

If I hover on someFunction() I see following hover which is having scope details. I am not sure if it makes sense to show scopes there

